"""
    List bundles in the cache
    """
bundle_dir = p(self.test_homedir, '.owmeta', 'bundles', 'test%2Fmain', '1')
makedirs(bundle_dir)
with open(p(bundle_dir, 'manifest'), 'w') as mf:
    mf.write('{"version": 1, "id": "test/main"}')
assertRegexpMatches(self.sh('owm bundle cache list'), 'test/main@1')
